# Root ignores. The app has its own .gitignore for build artifacts.

# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Business strategy — deliberately kept OUT of the repository
# ---------------------------------------------------------------------------
# The repo is intended to be public, because public repos get unlimited GitHub
# Actions minutes (which is what makes 15-minute history capture free) and
# because an open codebase is a genuine trust signal for a public-good health
# tool.
#
# None of that requires publishing revenue projections, pricing strategy, or the
# go-to-market playbook. Those files stay on local disk only.
#
# To publish them anyway, delete the two lines below and commit.
business/
research/

# Local environment
.env
.env.local
.env*.local

# Editor / OS noise
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/
*.swp
